 Sattyananda's Mind Expansion is an album that invites you to explore electronic music at its core.
 This album takes you on a journey through different styles of electronic music from 4x4 to breaks to chilled out spaces. It also features some heavy weights from the Indian fusion music scene like Shubha Mudgal, Pundit Ajay Prasanna, Pundit Mukesh Sharma & Pundit Bholenath Mishra. Mind Expansion talks about subjects ranging from extraterrestrial life, aliens conspiracies, space programs & spirituality.
 We invite you on this journey! Bring an open mind and enjoy.
